\v 5 <a name="00501400500002" ll="SDBH:אַיָּל:000000">鹿</a>​、​<a name="00501400500006" ll="SDBH:צְבִי:001000">羚</a>​、​<a name="00501400500010" ll="SDBH:יַחְמוּר:000000">麃子</a>​、​<a name="00501400500014" ll="SDBH:אַקֹּו:000000">野</a>​<a name="00501400500014" ll="SDBH:אַקֹּו:000000">山羊</a>​、​<a name="00501400500018" ll="SDBH:דִּישֹׁון:000000">瞪羚</a>​、​<a name="00501400500022" ll="SDBH:תְּאֹו:000000">羚羊</a>​、​<a name="00501400500026" ll="SDBH:זֶמֶר:000000">山</a>​<a name="00501400500026" ll="SDBH:זֶמֶר:000000">绵羊</a>​。 
